{"tid":743173,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"國足傳奇郝海東：關心屎朗還不如帶孩子去踢球","createTime":"2018-07-15T07:56:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T08:57:20.000Z","uid":20634,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6cb23dba8799897d0ce3334cb5763d4da1c728c6","tid":743173,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T07:56:56.000Z","msg":"近日，前國腳郝海東在參加一檔體育欄目時，再次談到了自己曾經有關&ldquo;C羅最多再火3年&rdquo;的言論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img1.dongqiudi.com/fastdfs3/M00/2D/EC/720x-/-/-/ChOxM1tKGqWAYll4AAD0HBgrFZ8677.jpg?watermark/1/image/aHR0cDovL2ltZzEuZG9uZ3FpdWRpLmNvbS9mYXN0ZGZzMi9NMDAvMkEvRTIvQ2hPcU0xb1MtZVdBUERxM0FBQkE1VWdyQlQ4MTQyLnBuZz9pbWFnZVZpZXcyLzAvdy8xMjA=/dissolve/100/dx/14/dy/10\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.dongqiudi.com%2Ffastdfs3%2FM00%2F2D%2FEC%2F720x-%2F-%2F-%2FChOxM1tKGqWAYll4AAD0HBgrFZ8677.jpg%3Fwatermark%2F1%2Fimage%2FaHR0cDovL2ltZzEuZG9uZ3FpdWRpLmNvbS9mYXN0ZGZzMi9NMDAvMkEvRTIvQ2hPcU0xb1MtZVdBUERxM0FBQkE1VWdyQlQ4MTQyLnBuZz9pbWFnZVZpZXcyLzAvdy8xMjA%3D%2Fdissolve%2F100%2Fdx%2F14%2Fdy%2F10&h=1d51f78b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n他表示：&ldquo;我當年講的他(C羅)火不過三五年是什麼(情況下說的呢)，當年的世界杯，他撥一腳完了就射啊，就是很遠的遠射，而且當時他們也沒得什麼成績嘛，是吧？只不過是你們拿了(當年)我說過的一句話來跟我老在這說。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;C羅，我們不否認他是一個勤奮的，而且有一定特點能力的一名球員，他的商業價值都在。當然，從他的競技能力(來說)的話，他已經在走下坡路了。如果不是(這樣的話)，皇馬不會這麼便宜地賣了他，對吧？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;國內的球迷，你看他的球啊、你高喊著他的名字的時候，他連(你是誰)什麼都不知道，是吧？他都沒見過你。你(應該)想想可以怎麼保障自己的'利益'，有自己的球場，帶孩子們去踢足球，你去幹幹這(種事情)。問郝海東'C羅能火多少年'跟你半毛錢關係都沒有。這沒有意義。我只想告訴你(球迷)一些真實的我關於足球的一些看法。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"80695be36be55eb63a06c96d1c84319a815bd526","tid":743173,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T08:01:36.000Z","msg":"wfc"},{"pid":"cd96cffe516685062f865244c06125597f4b25d8","tid":743173,"uid":110043,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T08:04:44.000Z","msg":"垃圾球員批評C朗?"},{"pid":"f4bdc0d945d98b2043b0264284b8aeda69a10d5e","tid":743173,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T08:11:00.000Z","msg":"係大陸就名宿可以也文也武，一出中國垃圾不如"},{"pid":"1cbe144dc9276721e76ffb399b7c3c59f84619b4","tid":743173,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd96cffe516685062f865244c06125597f4b25d8","tid":743173,"uid":110043,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T08:04:44.000Z","msg":"垃圾球員批評C朗?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T08:26:06.000Z","msg":"傳奇來，請尊重"},{"pid":"db3845a820cfee45b7c7918f38187f0b70ad3d08","tid":743173,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4bdc0d945d98b2043b0264284b8aeda69a10d5e","tid":743173,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T08:11:00.000Z","msg":"係大陸就名宿可以也文也武，一出中國垃圾不如"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T08:57:06.000Z","msg":"傳奇垃圾?"},{"pid":"d75d7af98fbe81ee7068da3fa65b642815dddc65","tid":743173,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cbe144dc9276721e76ffb399b7c3c59f84619b4","tid":743173,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd96cffe516685062f865244c06125597f4b25d8","tid":743173,"uid":110043,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T08:04:44.000Z","msg":"垃圾球員批評C朗?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T08:26:06.000Z","msg":"傳奇來，請尊重"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T08:57:20.000Z","msg":"傳奇垃圾?"}]}